# README

 AndroidRPT: Project to work with Open Movie DB and Android UI

# Building an apk
- Download repo, navigate to root directory
- Execute the "gradle clean build"
- find apk file under $PROJECT/app/build/outputs/apk/app-debug.apk

# Version 1.0
 - App opens with two tabs, one for Search and other for Favorites
 - Search bar is available on the top of the Tab.
 - Search text needs to be entered and submitted (by clicking "Return")
 - Movie details are populated in the list
 Limitations:
 - App does not show all the details (in detail view) when a movie is selected
   and favorites
 - DB is not being as of now to persist FAVORITE movies,
